WEBVTT

00:07.975 --> 00:09.376
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:09.409 --> 00:11.245
Silas: THE FUCK?!

00:11.278 --> 00:12.646
WHAT'S THE MATTER WITH YOU, MAN?
ARE YOU ON DRUGS?

00:12.679 --> 00:14.982
MY PARENTS HAVE BEEN DRUGGING ME
SINCE I WAS 13.

00:15.015 --> 00:16.650
JUST GIVE ME MY PLANTS,
MAN.

00:16.683 --> 00:18.785
UM, DO YOU HAVE
PLANS TONIGHT?

00:18.819 --> 00:21.188
