I'LL GET MY SKATES.

00:24.291 --> 00:26.727
I WAS HAVING SEX WITH THIS WOMAN
AT THE DERBY RINK.

00:26.760 --> 00:28.996
<i>YOU</i> BROKE UP WITH <i>ME.</i>

00:29.029 --> 00:29.997
IS THIS REAL‐LIFE?

00:30.030 --> 00:30.998
NO.
YOU'RE DREAMING.

00:31.031 --> 00:32.466
NOW GO HARDER.

00:32.499 --> 00:33.734
WHAT THE FUCK?!

00:33.767 --> 00:34.968
I GUESS WE'RE EVEN.

00:35.002 --> 00:36.737
PLEASE GO BACK
TO SCREWING ANDY.

00:36.770 --> 00:38.205
Jill:
WE HAVE NO MONEY.

00:38.238 --> 00:39.973
DOUG'S CASH IS ALL TIED UP
IN THAT FAKE CHARITY,

00:40.007 --> 00:42.242
AND, UH, YOU AND ANDY
DON'T MAKE DICK.

00:42.276 --> 00:44.111
WE'RE REALLY BROKE?
YEAH.

00:44.144 --> 00:45.512
MAYBE IT'S THE BULLET?

00:45.546 --> 00:47.447
I DON'T KNOW ‐‐
THIS JUST ISN'T ME ANYMORE.

00:47.481 --> 00:48.982
I'M GONNA NEED YOU
TO BUY ME OUT.

00:49.016 --> 00:52.486
I CAN'T KEEP MAKING
THE SAME CHOICES.

