02:00.140 --> 02:01.207
MM.

02:01.241 --> 02:03.643
BUT I'M OPEN.
I WANT TO WORK.

02:03.676 --> 02:06.846
WOW. YOU REALLY
CAN'T SEE A MARK.

02:06.880 --> 02:08.648
SORRY?

02:08.681 --> 02:10.917
OH, WHERE YOU GOT SHOT. I JUST
EXPECTED SOMETHING BIGGER.

02:10.950 --> 02:14.187
I MEAN NOT, LIKE, A HUGE,
GAPING HOLE, BUT I DON'T KNOW.

02:14.220 --> 02:16.222
A DENT,
A SPIDER CRACK.

02:16.256 --> 02:18.758
OH, UH, MY SECRETARY
FOUND THAT ARTICLE ABOUT YOU

02:18.792 --> 02:20.193
IN THE <i>OLD SANDWICH PRESS.</i>

02:20.226 --> 02:21.895
YOU KNOW, WE, UH ‐‐
WE PRE‐SCREEN EVERYONE WHO ‐‐

02:21.928 --> 02:24.431
WHO MAKES AN APPOINTMENT,
SO...

02:24.464 --> 02:26.733
I NEED A JOB, MR. BURKS.

02:26.766 --> 02:27.867
