02:27.901 --> 02:32.205
LISTEN, WE'RE A HIGH‐LEVEL
EXECUTIVE SEARCH FIRM,

02:32.238 --> 02:35.508
SO WE DEAL WITH C. E. O. s,
C. F. O. s, C. O. O.‐‐

02:35.542 --> 02:37.644
YOU TOOK
THIS APPOINTMENT.

02:37.677 --> 02:40.747
OKAY. FULL DISCLOSURE.
THE ARTICLE WAS A DOOZY.

02:40.780 --> 02:43.183
I MEAN, I WAS ‐‐
YOU KNOW, I WAS CURIOUS.

02:43.216 --> 02:46.119
IT WAS A MISTAKE.
I'M SORRY. MEA CULPA.

02:46.152 --> 02:48.054
THEN MAKE IT RIGHT.

02:48.088 --> 02:51.591
I'VE WORKED
WITH C. E. O. s, C. F. O. s.

02:51.624 --> 02:56.096
I'VE LED MY OWN SALES TEAM,
MARKETING, RE‐BRANDING.

02:56.129 --> 02:57.764
I‐I...

02:59.232 --> 03:00.633
JUST TELL ME
WHO TO TALK TO.

03:00.667 --> 03:02.635
JUST POINT ME
IN THE RIGHT DIRECTION.

03:02.669 --> 03:06.506
HEY, SHAKE THE TREES,
PUT YOURSELF OUT THERE,

03:06.539 --> 03:10.243
AND, UH,
KEEP YOUR HEAD DOWN.

03:17.350 --> 03:18.718
HOW LONG
YOU BEEN STANDING HERE?

03:18.751 --> 03:21.788
YOU ALWAYS HUM "HAVA NAGILA"
WHEN YOU JERK OFF?

03:21.821 --> 03:22.789
HA HA HA.

03:22.822 --> 03:24.824
[ HUMMING "HAVA NAGILA" ]

03:26.793 --> 03:29.829
YOU CAN'T MAKE ME FEEL ANY
GUILTIER ABOUT SCREWING DOUG.

03:29.863 --> 03:31.498
IT WAS WEEKS AGO.

03:31.531 --> 03:33.600
AND IF YOU THINK
IT WAS BAD FOR <i>YOU,</i>

03:33.633 --> 03:35.935
IMAGINE WHAT IT WAS LIKE
FOR ME.

03:35.969 --> 03:37.804
I'M PREGNANT.

03:37.837 --> 03:39.439
[ HUMMING STOPS ]

03:43.743 --> 03:46.579
WELL...
I WISH YOU BOTH THE BEST.

03:46.613 --> 03:48.148
I'M SURE YOU AND DOUG
WILL HAVE A GREAT BABY

03:48.181 --> 03:49.649
AND A GREAT LIFE TOGETHER.

03:49.682 --> 03:52.118
NOW I'M GONNA GO
LAY UNDER A BLANKET.

03:52.152 --> 03:54.053
IT'S NOT DOUG'S.

03:54.087 --> 03:56.423
ANDY?

03:56.456 --> 03:59.626
YOU'RE SWEATING.
[ CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY ]

03:59.659 --> 04:02.262
THERE'S A VERY REAL LACK
OF AIR FLOW IN THIS HALLWAY.

04:02.295 --> 04:04.798
THERE'S, LIKE, NOTHING
COMING OUT OF THESE VENTS.

04:04.831 --> 04:05.865
NOTHING.

04:05.899 --> 04:07.700
THAT'S A RETURN.

04:07.734 --> 04:08.768
OH. [ SCOFFS ]

04:08.802 --> 04:10.970
WELL, YOU'VE GOT IT
ALL FIGURED OUT.

04:11.004 --> 04:12.205
