FIGURED OUT.

04:12.238 --> 04:13.440
AND WHEN I SAID
IT WASN'T DOUG'S,

04:13.473 --> 04:16.075
THAT'S JUST A GUESS ‐‐
A HOPE, REALLY.

04:16.109 --> 04:21.214
BUT I'M...ALMOST
FOR SURE PREGNANT.

04:21.247 --> 04:24.217
AT LEAST
IT FEELS THAT WAY.

04:24.250 --> 04:26.319
MAZEL TOV?

04:32.192 --> 04:34.294
[ WHISTLE BLOWS ]

04:34.327 --> 04:36.729
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

04:47.006 --> 04:49.409
[ WHISTLE BLOWS ]

04:55.615 --> 05:00.320
GOT TO LOVE
ORGANIZED CHAOS.

05:00.353 --> 05:04.457
YEAH. THEY'RE LIKE MOLECULES
ALL BOUNCING AROUND.

05:04.491 --> 05:08.294
OR TRIPPING THEMSELVES,
IN THE CASE OF MY SON.

05:08.328 --> 05:10.096
SHAKE IT OFF, CHAMP!

05:10.130 --> 05:12.499
UH, MAYBE THERE WAS
A SPRINKLER HEAD?

05:12.532 --> 05:15.802
IF ONLY.
BUT THANK YOU.

05:15.835 --> 05:16.970
I'M, UH ‐‐ I'M TERRY.

05:17.003 --> 05:18.271
NANCY.

05:18.304 --> 05:22.809
GONNA HAVE TO MAKE
A CITIZEN'S ARREST.

05:22.842 --> 05:23.843
EXCUSE ME?

05:23.877 --> 05:25.912
THE HAND‐OFF?

05:25.945 --> 05:28.481
YOU SHOULD HAVE HID IT
IN THE MAGAZINE.
OH.

05:28.515 --> 05:30.550
THAT'S WHAT
THAT LOOKED LIKE?

05:30.583 --> 05:31.351
OH, BOY.

05:31.384 --> 05:32.452
OH, NO. RELAX.

05:32.485 --> 05:34.320
IT'S NONE
OF MY BUSINESS.

05:34.354 --> 05:36.022
NO, NO, NO, NO.
[ CHUCKLES ] NO, NO.

05:36.055 --> 05:37.557
IT'S...

05:37.590 --> 05:41.194
FRANK'S GOT A PROSTATE
THE SIZE OF A V. W.

05:41.227 --> 05:44.364
THE GUY NEXT TO HIM, ROG,
HE'S GOT A, UH, FUNGUS

05:44.397 --> 05:46.366
