IN MIXED COMPANY,

05:46.399 --> 05:47.634
BUT IT'S NOT GOOD.

05:47.667 --> 05:51.938
ProstiFlo FOR FRANK,
ZYCOPRIL FOR ROG.

05:51.971 --> 05:53.506
OH,
SO IT'S DR. TERRY.

05:53.540 --> 05:56.509
NOT EXACTLY.

05:59.479 --> 06:03.116
YOU'RE THE BIGGEST
DRUG DEALER IN TOWN.

06:03.149 --> 06:04.250
[ CHUCKLES ]

06:04.284 --> 06:06.786
YEAH.
LEGAL ONE, ANYWAY.

06:06.820 --> 06:08.955
CARE FOR A JUICE BOX?

06:08.988 --> 06:11.991
THANK YOU.

06:14.561 --> 06:15.795
[ BUZZER ]

06:15.829 --> 06:17.464
[ TAPPING ]

06:17.497 --> 06:20.767
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

06:26.840 --> 06:28.208
JABBERWOCKY!

06:28.241 --> 06:29.642
10.78 SECONDS.

06:29.676 --> 06:30.777
[ CHUCKLES ]

06:30.810 --> 06:32.846
OH, HEY, SILAS.
DO YOU LIKE SPORT STACKING?

06:32.879 --> 06:34.914
WHAT THE FUCK?

06:34.948 --> 06:36.716
DO YOU WANT TO TRY
A CYCLE?

06:36.749 --> 06:37.884
WANT TO TRY A CYCLE?

06:37.917 --> 06:40.787
