ON FOURSQUARE.
YEAH, I GOT THAT.

06:42.989 --> 06:46.059
NOW, NUTBALLS,
YOU STOLE MY PLANTS.

06:46.092 --> 06:47.427
AND THAT'S A TOTAL
"MY BAD."

06:47.460 --> 06:48.962
BUT THE GOOD NEWS IS,
I'M BACK ON MY MEDS,

06:48.995 --> 06:50.663
SO THAT
WON'T HAPPEN AGAIN.

06:50.697 --> 06:52.298
WHERE ARE THEY?
THEY'RE, LIKE, LOCKED
IN A CABINET SOMEWHERE.

06:52.332 --> 06:54.234
THE NURSE DISTRIBUTES THEM
TWICE A DAY, SO ‐‐

06:54.267 --> 06:55.468
[ SMACKS TABLE ]
MY PLANTS.

06:55.502 --> 06:56.569
OH.

06:56.603 --> 06:58.071
THEY'RE IN A CLOSET
AT MY PARENTS' HOUSE.

06:58.104 --> 07:00.106
B‐BUT THEY'RE FINE.
I LEFT SOME LIGHTS ON.

07:00.140 --> 07:01.975
OH, YOU LEFT
A COUPLE LIGHTS.

07:02.008 --> 07:03.476
LET'S GO.

07:03.510 --> 07:05.478
I'M STILL ON PSYCH HOLD.
I CAN'T GO ANYWHERE.
OKAY.

07:05.512 --> 07:07.213
UH, WHY DON'T YOU TELL ME
WHERE YOUR PARENTS LIVE,

07:07.247 --> 07:09.482
AND I'LL GO GET THEM
MYSELF?
NO WAY.

07:09.516 --> 07:11.584
MY PARENTS FREAK IF
ONE OF MY DRUG FRIENDS SHOWS UP.

07:13.119 --> 07:14.587
I NEED MY PLANTS.

07:14.621 --> 07:16.122
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT TO TELL YOU.

07:16.156 --> 07:18.091
I'M REALLY SORRY, SILAS.
I‐I WASN'T MYSELF.

07:18.124 --> 07:19.459
I MEAN I WAS MYSELF.

07:19.492 --> 07:22.562
I JUST WASN'T MY ‐‐
MY MEDICATED SELF. I‐I...

07:22.595 --> 07:25.331
DO YOU WANT TO LEARN
HOW TO STACK?

07:25.365 --> 07:28.768
OKAY. NEVER MIND.

07:30.236 --> 07:31.337
