07:31.371 --> 07:33.940
95%.
STATUTES ARE MY BITCH.

07:33.973 --> 07:35.442
97%.

07:35.475 --> 07:37.343
SPANKED IT, SPANKED YOU.

07:37.377 --> 07:40.246
MIGHT EVEN SPANK MYSELF
I'M SO GOOD.

07:40.280 --> 07:41.981
