SHOULD TAKE ME OUT TO DINNER.

07:45.685 --> 07:47.253
Roberson:
ATTENTION, EVERYONE.

07:47.287 --> 07:50.090
WELL,
EXCEPT FOR A COUPLE OF YOU

07:50.123 --> 07:51.691
THAT FELL
OUTSIDE THE BELL CURVE,

07:51.724 --> 07:54.761
