YOU'RE SO STUPID.

07:57.130 --> 07:59.766
I DON'T KNOW.
IT IS UNFORTUNATE.

07:59.799 --> 08:03.570
SO, TO HELP YOU COMBAT THAT,
I WANT YOU TO WRITE AN ESSAY.

08:03.603 --> 08:06.106
500 WORDS
DUE TOMORROW MORNING ‐‐

08:06.139 --> 08:08.675
"WHY DO I
DESERVE TO BE A COP?"

08:08.708 --> 08:11.144
PSST.
YEAH?

08:11.177 --> 08:14.714
WHY YOU DESERVE TO BE A COP
OR I, LIKE ME?

08:14.747 --> 08:17.717
WHATEVER YOU THINK IS BEST,
RONCHETTA.

08:17.750 --> 08:21.955
NOW, I DON'T WANT TO BE HERE
ANYMORE.

08:25.925 --> 08:28.828
BYE, LOSER.

08:28.862 --> 08:30.230
