DOWN THE DRAIN.

08:30.263 --> 08:31.765
AND IT'S
TEJADA BOBBLEHEAD NIGHT.

08:31.798 --> 08:34.434
MAN, I WAS GONNA
TAKE MY GIRL TO B‐DUBS.

08:34.467 --> 08:37.971
SOMETHING ABOUT EATING HOT WINGS
JUST MOVES HER JUICES.

08:38.004 --> 08:39.339
[ CHUCKLES ]

08:39.372 --> 08:40.907
I'LL WRITE YOUR ESSAYS.

08:42.142 --> 08:43.209
100 BUCKS EACH.

08:43.243 --> 08:45.678
[ SCOFFS ]
100 BUCKS?

08:45.712 --> 08:47.247
FUCK OFF, BOTWIN.

08:47.280 --> 08:49.983
I'M JUST TRYING TO HELP ‐‐
BOBBLEHEADS, JUICES.

08:51.651 --> 08:54.487
ALL RIGHT.

08:56.222 --> 08:58.158
Man: AUSTIN! GOOD!

08:58.191 --> 08:59.726
YOU WON!
GO OUT AGAIN, ETHAN!

08:59.759 --> 09:02.796
THEY ALL HATE ME
'CAUSE STEVIE'S SO GOOD.

09:02.829 --> 09:04.063
MM‐HMM.

09:04.097 --> 09:07.233
