TO HAVE A FRIEND.

10:08.495 --> 10:11.965
WE HAVEN'T HAD A NIGHT
TO OURSELVES IN THREE YEARS.

10:13.500 --> 10:16.469
YOU KNOW THAT'S WHAT
NANNIES AND SITTERS ARE FOR.

10:16.503 --> 10:19.606
[ SIGHS ]
THEY ALL TALK.

10:19.639 --> 10:21.374
IT'S LIKE A SECRET,
LITTLE CLUB.

10:21.407 --> 10:25.512
ONCE YOU GET BLACKLISTED,
YOU'RE SCREWED.

10:25.545 --> 10:29.582
SO HE'S ‐‐ HE'S ‐‐ HE'S...
HE'S GOT A FEW QUIRKS.

10:29.616 --> 10:31.785
