10:31.818 --> 10:33.586
ONE SLEEPOVER ‐‐ TONIGHT.

10:33.620 --> 10:35.155
AND I WILL CALL
MY COLLEAGUE IN SALES ‐‐

10:35.188 --> 10:37.290
RECOMMEND HE HIRE
A NEW SALES REP.

10:37.323 --> 10:40.493
