ONE SLEEPOVER?

10:40.527 --> 10:41.494
OKAY.

10:41.528 --> 10:42.629
YES. YES.

10:42.662 --> 10:44.898
MY WIFE ‐‐
I'M GONNA CALL HER RIGHT NOW.

10:44.931 --> 10:46.332
OH!

10:46.366 --> 10:48.568
