ON THE WAY HOME.

10:57.739 --> 10:59.801
UGH. SHIT.

11:00.860 --> 11:03.619
ALL RIGHT. ENOUGH
OF THIS FAGGY SILENT TREATMENT.

11:03.652 --> 11:05.788
LET'S GET IT
OUT IN THE OPEN.

11:05.821 --> 11:08.357
YES, I FUCKED THE SHIT
OUT OF JILL.

11:08.390 --> 11:10.226
THAT WAS PROBABLY NOT COOL.

11:10.259 --> 11:11.760
SHE MIGHT BE PREGNANT.

11:11.794 --> 11:12.928
[ BALLS CLACK ]

11:12.962 --> 11:14.630
