NOT AN EIGHT BALL.

11:38.621 --> 11:41.657
NO, I MEAN
FOR WHO TAKES IT ALL ON.

11:41.690 --> 11:45.094
NICE. REAL NICE.

11:45.127 --> 11:46.162
[ SIGHS ]

11:46.195 --> 11:48.130
