DARTS? NO. NO DARTBOARD.

11:48.164 --> 11:51.200
FUCK! WE DON'T EVEN KNOW
IF SHE'S PREGNANT YET.

11:51.233 --> 11:53.202
YES, WE DO.

11:54.537 --> 11:56.772
SO, DOES THE WINNER
GET ME AND THE KID

11:56.805 --> 11:59.241
OR IS THAT THE LOSER?

11:59.275 --> 12:01.010
ASSHOLES.

12:06.015 --> 12:08.017
I'LL RACK.

12:09.718 --> 12:11.854
[ DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

12:41.417 --> 12:43.752
[ LOCK CLICKS ]

12:49.525 --> 12:51.393
SURPRISE!SURPRISE!
SURPRISE!SURPRISE!

12:52.661 --> 12:55.097
Man:
WHO THE FUCK?

12:55.130 --> 12:56.098
REALLY, SUZE?

12:56.131 --> 12:57.900
DOES EVERY OCCASION
NEED A STRIPPER?

12:57.933 --> 13:00.836
HE WAS SUPPOSED TO BE
A COP.

13:00.870 --> 13:05.374
UH, IT'S A WHOLE THING
THAT WE DO.

13:05.407 --> 13:07.176
BRING IN A ROBBER.
LESS TALKING.

